<PageShell
  title="Health Insurance for Retirees in Italy | Elective Residency Guide 2026"
  description="Complete guide to health insurance for retirees in Italy. Compare international plans meeting Schengen visa requirements with pre-existing condition coverage and age 65+ acceptance."
  headline="Health Insurance for Retirees in Italy"
  subheadline="Your guide to comprehensive health coverage with Italy's elective residency visa"
